					p México | Carlos Saucedo | saucedoc@mx1.ibm.com
				.col-md-6
					p.font-weight-bold IBM Open Badge Program
					p.m-0 Información general del badge: 
						a(href="https://www.youracclaim.com/org/ibm/badge/tjbot-teacher-advocate") Your Acclaim
					p Contacto: badge@us.ibm.com

