			.row
				.col-md-12.mt-md-0.mt-3
					h5.text-uppercase.font-weight-bold.text-justify.text-center Privacy statement.
					p.text-justify.text-center
					| NOTICE: IBM leverages the services of Credly's Acclaim platform, a 3rd party data processor authorized by IBM 
