					| to issue you an IBM Digital Badge, your personal information (name, email address, and badge earned) will be 
					| shared with the Credly’s Acclaim platform.  You will receive an email notification from Acclaim with instructions 
					| for claiming the badge. Your personal information is used to issue your badge and for program reporting and operational 
					| purposes. It will be handled in a manner consistent with IBM privacy practices.  The IBM Privacy Statement can be viewed 
					| here:  
					a(href='https://www.ibm.com/privacy/us/en') https://www.ibm.com/privacy/us/en/.   
